    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"816344\">Aaron Liu</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/113488-general/topic/Function.20giving.20type.20mismatch.20on.20output/near/570665755\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>what exactly do you mean \"get them out\"</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>As in, getting rid of the angled brackets. I can't do much with the brackets in the goal.</p>\n<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"307953\">Ruben Van de Velde</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/113488-general/topic/Function.20giving.20type.20mismatch.20on.20output/near/570665688\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code>generalize_proofs</code> perhaps</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>That's added the subtype proof for <code>k</code> as a hypothesis, but the brackets remain.</p>",
        "id": 570666211,
        "sender_full_name": "Tarun Nair",
        "timestamp": 1769636885
